flights

Class AirlineTicket

  • java.lang.Object
    • flights.AirlineTicket

  • public class AirlineTicket
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a ticket on a flight. I contains a reference to the customer that this ticket belongs to, the flight the ticket is for, and the price of the ticket. Assumptions/Restrictions: None. Noteworthy Features: Applying points to customers (and taking away points if a mistake was made) happens automatically in the set passenger method.
    Author:
    Ryan Amaral
